        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Those who are left in Zion, who remain in Jerusalem, will be called holy, all who are recorded among the living in Jerusalem."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "All who remain in Zion will be a holy people— those who survive the destruction of Jerusalem and are recorded among the living."
